<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body 
of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Author&#8217;s name. &#34;Title of Article.&#34; <em>Name of Publication</em> 
	volume.issue (year of publication): page numbers. Medium of publication.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s name">Smith, Albaraa</span>. 
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of Article">High Speed Compression for Music Downloads</span>.&#34; 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Name of Publication">Journal of Internet Engineering</span></em> 
	<span class="hover" title="volume">10</span>.<span class="hover" title="issue">2</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="year of publication">2056</span>): 
	<span class="hover" title="page numbers">154&#45;165</span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Medium of publication">Print</span>.
</blockquote>
